data.value:
How to get the best grade in the Math Quiz: • You get +50 points for answering the 4 expressions correctly. • If you finish the quiz before the countdown you will get +50 points. • For every wrong answer you get -5 points. • For every 30 seconds you play after the end of the countdown you get -5 points. • Your grade can't be negative.
Other Information: • After the end of the countdown you can use a calculator but you can only use 2 expressions!
